.TH AGENT-HOOK-SESSION-END 1 "2026-06-30" "agentguard" "User Commands"
.SH NAME
agent-hook-session-end \- run generic agent session-end maintenance
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B agent-hook-session-end
.SH DESCRIPTION
.B agent-hook-session-end
reads a session-end hook JSON payload from standard input, refreshes shared
session metadata, and gives extensions a final chance to run agent or
environment-specific maintenance.
.SH EXIT STATUS
.TP
.B 0
Session-end maintenance completed.
.SH SEE ALSO
.BR agent-hook-session-end-claude (1)
